    "title": "Looking for Software Engineer at mfine Global Group",
    "description": "mfine Global Group, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Software Engineer for our Bhubaneswar operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout mfine Global Group:\nmfine Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Flexible working hours\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with mfine Global Group!",
